column1: #Text=To help prevent spread of COVID -19 ,procedures and supplies should be in place to encourage proper hand and respiratory hygiene as well as routine cleaning and disinfection of high -risk locations .
#Text=This guidance is provided for any local or state public or private facility so that owners ,operators and other individuals can incorporate these procedures into their facility protocols .
#Text=High -risk locations (see below )warrant cleaning and disinfection on a regular schedule .
